{"tid":1650812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蝙蝠俠(1)的一段電影對白","createTime":"2019-10-13T06:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T06:52:14.000Z","uid":2719,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"17916c49606abf08f7c130dbe3fab80aa0239422","tid":1650812,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:52:14.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>蝙蝠俠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />                        教練<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><ins><strong>教練﹕</strong></ins><br />\n你父母嘅死唔係你嘅錯，係你爸爸嘅錯。<br />\n你根本改變唔到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你爸爸咁懦弱嘅事實！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>蝙蝠俠﹕</strong></ins><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢(殺人犯)攞嘅槍架。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>教練﹕</strong></ins><br />\n阻止到你咩？<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>蝙蝠俠﹕</strong></ins><br />\n我受過訓練。<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>教練﹕</strong></ins><br />\n受訓又點啊？重點係<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">意志，係出擊嘅意志！</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">( 唔可以縱容壞人，打擊佢地，唔可以猶豫，唔可以留情！ )</div></strong></span>"}]}